        "Pricing Schedule": ["Provide clear and transparent pricing structure", "Align pricing with budget allowed for tender", "Explain any pricing assumptions or exclusions", "Show breakdown of costs relative to fair market value"],
        "Pricing Rationale": ["Provide clear and transparent pricing structure", "Align pricing with budget allowed for tender", "Explain any pricing assumptions or exclusions", "Demonstrate value for money compared to competitors"],
        "Relevant Experience": ["Demonstrate success in similar projects using STAR format", "Include quantifiable outcomes and testimonials", "Cite innovative solutions from past work", "Highlight relevant awards"],
